{"thi-ap30:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap30:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap30:0.3":"10 Yasodharapamukhaattharasabhikkhunisahassaapadana ","thi-ap30:1.1":"Attharasasahassani, ","thi-ap30:1.2":"bhikkhuni sakyasambhava; ","thi-ap30:1.3":"Yasodharapamukhani, ","thi-ap30:1.4":"sambuddham upasankamum. ","thi-ap30:2.1":"Attharasasahassani, ","thi-ap30:2.2":"sabba honti mahiddhika; ","thi-ap30:2.3":"Vandanti munino pade, ","thi-ap30:2.4":"arocenti yathabalam. ","thi-ap30:3.1":"“Jati khina jara byadhi, ","thi-ap30:3.2":"marananca mahamuni; ","thi-ap30:3.3":"Anasavam padam santam, ","thi-ap30:3.4":"amatam yama nayaka. ","thi-ap30:4.1":"Khalitance pure atthi, ","thi-ap30:4.2":"sabbasampi mahamuni; ","thi-ap30:4.3":"Aparadhamajananti, ","thi-ap30:4.4":"khama amham vinayaka”. ","thi-ap30:5.1":"“Iddhincapi nidassetha, ","thi-ap30:5.2":"mama sasanakarika; ","thi-ap30:5.3":"Parisananca sabbasam, ","thi-ap30:5.4":"kankham chindatha yavata”. ","thi-ap30:6.1":"“Yasodhara mahavira, ","thi-ap30:6.2":"manapa piyadassana; ","thi-ap30:6.3":"Sabba tuyham mahavira, ","thi-ap30:6.4":"agarasmim pajapati. ","thi-ap30:7.1":"Thinam satasahassanam, ","thi-ap30:7.2":"navutinam chaduttari; ","thi-ap30:7.3":"Agare te mayam vira, ","thi-ap30:7.4":"pamokkha sabba issara. ","thi-ap30:8.1":"Rupacaragunupeta, ","thi-ap30:8.2":"yobbanattha piyamvada; ","thi-ap30:8.3":"Sabba no apacayanti, ","thi-ap30:8.4":"devata viya manusa. ","thi-ap30:9.1":"Attharasasahassani, ","thi-ap30:9.2":"sabba sakiyasambhava; ","thi-ap30:9.3":"Yasodharasahassani, ","thi-ap30:9.4":"pamokkha issara tada. ","thi-ap30:10.1":"Kamadhatumatikkamma, ","thi-ap30:10.2":"santhita rupadhatuya; ","thi-ap30:10.3":"Rupena sadisa natthi, ","thi-ap30:10.4":"sahassanam mahamuni”. ","thi-ap30:11.1":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","thi-ap30:11.2":"iddhim dassamsu satthuno; ","thi-ap30:11.3":"Neka nanavidhakara, ","thi-ap30:11.4":"mahaiddhipi dassayum. ","thi-ap30:12.1":"Cakkavalasamam kayam, ","thi-ap30:12.2":"sisam uttarato kuru; ","thi-ap30:12.3":"Ubho pakkha duve dipa, ","thi-ap30:12.4":"jambudipam sarirato. ","thi-ap30:13.1":"Dakkhinanca saram pincham, ","thi-ap30:13.2":"nanasakha tu pattaka; ","thi-ap30:13.3":"Candanca suriyancakkhi, ","thi-ap30:13.4":"merupabbatato sikham. ","thi-ap30:14.1":"Cakkavalagirim tundam, ","thi-ap30:14.2":"jamburukkham samulakam; ","thi-ap30:14.3":"Bijamana upagantva, ","thi-ap30:14.4":"vandanti lokanayakam. ","thi-ap30:15.1":"Hatthivannam tathevassam, ","thi-ap30:15.2":"pabbatam jaladhim tatha; ","thi-ap30:15.3":"Candanca suriyam merum, ","thi-ap30:15.4":"sakkavannanca dassayum. ","thi-ap30:16.1":"“Yasodhara mayam vira, ","thi-ap30:16.2":"pade vandama cakkhuma; ","thi-ap30:16.3":"Tava cirapabhavena, ","thi-ap30:16.4":"nipphanna naranayaka. ","thi-ap30:17.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homa, ","thi-ap30:17.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap30:17.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap30:17.4":"vasi homa mahamune. ","thi-ap30:18.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap30:18.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap30:18.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap30:18.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap30:19.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap30:19.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap30:19.3":"Nanam amham mahavira, ","thi-ap30:19.4":"uppannam tava santike. ","thi-ap30:20.1":"Pubbanam lokanathanam, ","thi-ap30:20.2":"sangamam no nidassitam; ","thi-ap30:20.3":"Adhikara bahu amham, ","thi-ap30:20.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:21.1":"Yam amham puritam kammam, ","thi-ap30:21.2":"kusalam sarase mune; ","thi-ap30:21.3":"Tuyhatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap30:21.4":"punnanupacitani no. ","thi-ap30:22.1":"Abhabbatthane vajjetva, ","thi-ap30:22.2":"varayimha anacaram; ","thi-ap30:22.3":"Tuyhatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap30:22.4":"cattani jivitani no. ","thi-ap30:23.1":"Nekakotisahassani, ","thi-ap30:23.2":"bhariyatthayadasi no; ","thi-ap30:23.3":"Na tattha vimana homa, ","thi-ap30:23.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:24.1":"Nekakotisahassani, ","thi-ap30:24.2":"upakarayadasi no; ","thi-ap30:24.3":"Na tattha vimana homa, ","thi-ap30:24.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:25.1":"Nekakotisahassani, ","thi-ap30:25.2":"bhojanatthayadasi no; ","thi-ap30:25.3":"Na tattha vimana homa, ","thi-ap30:25.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:26.1":"Nekakotisahassani, ","thi-ap30:26.2":"jivitani cajimhase; ","thi-ap30:26.3":"Bhayamokkham karissama, ","thi-ap30:26.4":"jivitani cajimhase. ","thi-ap30:27.1":"Angagate alankare, ","thi-ap30:27.2":"vatthe nanavidhe bahu; ","thi-ap30:27.3":"Itthibhande na guhama, ","thi-ap30:27.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:28.1":"Dhanadhannapariccagam, ","thi-ap30:28.2":"gamani nigamani ca; ","thi-ap30:28.3":"Khettam putta ca dhita ca, ","thi-ap30:28.4":"pariccatta mahamune. ","thi-ap30:29.1":"Hatthi assa gava capi, ","thi-ap30:29.2":"dasiyo paricarika; ","thi-ap30:29.3":"Tuyhatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap30:29.4":"pariccattam asankhiyam. ","thi-ap30:30.1":"Yam amhe patimantesi, ","thi-ap30:30.2":"‘danam dassama yacake’; ","thi-ap30:30.3":"Vimanam no na passama, ","thi-ap30:30.4":"dadato danamuttamam. ","thi-ap30:31.1":"Nanavidham bahum dukkham, ","thi-ap30:31.2":"samsare ca bahubbidhe; ","thi-ap30:31.3":"Tuyhatthaya mahavira, ","thi-ap30:31.4":"anubhuttam asankhiyam. ","thi-ap30:32.1":"Sukhappattanumodama, ","thi-ap30:32.2":"na ca dukkhesu dummana; ","thi-ap30:32.3":"Sabbattha tulita homa, ","thi-ap30:32.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap30:33.1":"Anumaggena sambuddho, ","thi-ap30:33.2":"yam dhammam abhinihari; ","thi-ap30:33.3":"Anubhotva sukham dukkham, ","thi-ap30:33.4":"patto bodhim mahamune. ","thi-ap30:34.1":"Brahmadevanca sambuddham, ","thi-ap30:34.2":"gotamam lokanayakam; ","thi-ap30:34.3":"Annesam lokanathanam, ","thi-ap30:34.4":"sangamam tehi no bahu. ","thi-ap30:35.1":"Adhikaram bahum amhe, ","thi-ap30:35.2":"tuyhatthaya mahamune; ","thi-ap30:35.3":"Gavesato buddhadhamme, ","thi-ap30:35.4":"mayam te paricarika. ","thi-ap30:36.1":"Kappe ca satasahasse, ","thi-ap30:36.2":"caturo ca asankhiye; ","thi-ap30:36.3":"Dipankaro mahaviro, ","thi-ap30:36.4":"uppajji lokanayako. ","thi-ap30:37.1":"Paccantadesavisaye, ","thi-ap30:37.2":"nimantetva tathagatam; ","thi-ap30:37.3":"Tassa agamanam maggam, ","thi-ap30:37.4":"sodhenti tutthamanasa. ","thi-ap30:38.1":"Tena kalena so asi, ","thi-ap30:38.2":"sumedho nama brahmano; ","thi-ap30:38.3":"Magganca patiyadesi, ","thi-ap30:38.4":"ayato sabbadassino. ","thi-ap30:39.1":"Tena kalena ahumha, ","thi-ap30:39.2":"sabba brahmanasambhava; ","thi-ap30:39.3":"Thaludajani pupphani, ","thi-ap30:39.4":"aharimha samagamam. ","thi-ap30:40.1":"Tasmim so samaye buddho, ","thi-ap30:40.2":"dipankaro mahayaso; ","thi-ap30:40.3":"Viyakasi mahaviro, ","thi-ap30:40.4":"isimuggatamanasam. ","thi-ap30:41.1":"Calati ravati puthavi, ","thi-ap30:41.2":"sankampati sadevake; ","thi-ap30:41.3":"Tassa kammam pakittente, ","thi-ap30:41.4":"isimuggatamanasam. ","thi-ap30:42.1":"Devakanna manussa ca, ","thi-ap30:42.2":"mayancapi sadevaka; ","thi-ap30:42.3":"Nanapujaniyam bhandam, ","thi-ap30:42.4":"pujayitvana patthayum. ","thi-ap30:43.1":"Tesam buddho viyakasi, ","thi-ap30:43.2":"jotidipa sanamako; ","thi-ap30:43.3":"‘Ajja ye patthita atthi, ","thi-ap30:43.4":"te bhavissanti sammukha’. ","thi-ap30:44.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","thi-ap30:44.2":"yam no buddho viyakari; ","thi-ap30:44.3":"Tam vacamanumodenta, ","thi-ap30:44.4":"evankari ahumha no. ","thi-ap30:45.1":"Tassa kammassa sukatassa, ","thi-ap30:45.2":"tassa cittam pasadayum; ","thi-ap30:45.3":"Devamanusikam yonim, ","thi-ap30:45.4":"anubhotva asankhiyam. ","thi-ap30:46.1":"Sukhadukkhenubhotvana, ","thi-ap30:46.2":"devesu manusesu ca; ","thi-ap30:46.3":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap30:46.4":"jatamha sakiye kule. ","thi-ap30:47.1":"Rupavati bhogavati, ","thi-ap30:47.2":"yasasilavati tato; ","thi-ap30:47.3":"Sabbangasampada homa, ","thi-ap30:47.4":"kulesu abhisakkata. ","thi-ap30:48.1":"Labham silokam sakkaram, ","thi-ap30:48.2":"lokadhammasamagamam; ","thi-ap30:48.3":"Cittanca dukkhitam natthi, ","thi-ap30:48.4":"vasama akutobhaya. ","thi-ap30:49.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata, ","thi-ap30:49.2":"‘ranno antepure tada; ","thi-ap30:49.3":"Khattiyanam pure vira, ","thi-ap30:49.4":"upakaranca niddisi. ","thi-ap30:50.1":"Upakara ca ya nari, ","thi-ap30:50.2":"ya ca nari sukhe dukhe; ","thi-ap30:50.3":"Atthakkhayi ca ya nari, ","thi-ap30:50.4":"ya ca narinukampika. ","thi-ap30:51.1":"Dhammam care sucaritam, ","thi-ap30:51.2":"na nam duccaritam care; ","thi-ap30:51.3":"Dhammacari sukham seti, ","thi-ap30:51.4":"asmim loke paramhi ca’. ","thi-ap30:52.1":"Agaram vijahitvana, ","thi-ap30:52.2":"pabbajimhanagariyam; ","thi-ap30:52.3":"Addhamase asampatte, ","thi-ap30:52.4":"catusaccam phusimha no. ","thi-ap30:53.1":"Civaram pindapatanca, ","thi-ap30:53.2":"paccayam sayanasanam; ","thi-ap30:53.3":"Upanenti bahu amhe, ","thi-ap30:53.4":"sagarasseva umiyo. ","thi-ap30:54.1":"Kilesa jhapita amham, ","thi-ap30:54.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","thi-ap30:54.3":"Nagiva bandhanam chetva, ","thi-ap30:54.4":"viharama anasava. ","thi-ap30:55.1":"Svagatam vata no asi, ","thi-ap30:55.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","thi-ap30:55.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thi-ap30:55.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap30:56.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap30:56.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","thi-ap30:56.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thi-ap30:56.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap30:57.1":"Evam bahuvidham dukkham, ","thi-ap30:57.2":"sampatti ca bahubbidha; ","thi-ap30:57.3":"Visuddhabhavam sampatta, ","thi-ap30:57.4":"labhama sabbasampada. ","thi-ap30:58.1":"Ya dadanti sakattanam, ","thi-ap30:58.2":"punnatthaya mahesino; ","thi-ap30:58.3":"Sahayasampada honti, ","thi-ap30:58.4":"nibbanapadamasankhatam. ","thi-ap30:59.1":"Parikkhinam atitanca, ","thi-ap30:59.2":"paccuppannam anagatam; ","thi-ap30:59.3":"Sabbakammampi no khinam, ","thi-ap30:59.4":"pade vandama cakkhuma”. ","thi-ap30:60.1":"“Nibbanaya vadantinam, ","thi-ap30:60.2":"Kim vo vakkhama uttari; ","thi-ap30:60.3":"Santasankhatadosanhi, ","thi-ap30:60.4":"Pappotha amatam padam”. ","thi-ap30:61.1":"Ittham sudam yasodharapamukhani attharasabhikkhunisahassani bhagavato sammukha ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap30:62.1":"Yasodharapamukhaattharasabhikkhunisahassapadanam dasamam. ","thi-ap30:63.1":"Kundalakesivaggo tatiyo. ","thi-ap30:64.1":"Tassuddanam ","thi-ap30:65.1":"Kundala gotami ceva, ","thi-ap30:65.2":"dhammadinna ca sakula; ","thi-ap30:65.3":"Varananda ca sona ca, ","thi-ap30:65.4":"kapilani yasodhara. ","thi-ap30:66.1":"Dasasahassabhikkhuni, ","thi-ap30:66.2":"attharasasahassaka; ","thi-ap30:66.3":"Gathasatani cattari, ","thi-ap30:66.4":"cha ca sattatimeva ca. "}